<p>There are 2 columns where 1 - fixed 2 - dynamic (non-fixed)</p>    <pre class="lang-css prettyprint-override"><code>body {   height: 100%; } #left {   width: 55%;   float: left; } #right {   width: 45%;   height: 100vh;   position: fixed;   right: 0px; } </code></pre>  <p>Problem: For example text that I write in fixed column does not fit on height , and I want to make 1 scroll for 2 blocks, not (<code>overflow-y:scroll</code>), </p>  <p>How to scroll fixed column too while it's not end and in same time scroll non-fixed? </p>  <p><a href="http://jsfiddle.net/fL4f81ad/2/" rel="nofollow"><strong>JSfiddle Demo</strong></a></p>